title: Are You in Control of Your Life?
itunes:title: Are You in Control of Your Life?
description:
How intentional are you with your life? Most people don't realize that the majority of their day is spent in reaction mode, simply just putting out fires. In this episode, I am going to teach you how to be more intentional and in control of your life.
